oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Results of yield trials with spring barley
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Jensen, Jakob Willas
Deneken, Gerhard
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Cereals, pulses and oilseeds
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Trials with spring barley has been conducted on a farmers certified field. The varieties were grown after local standards as the farmer would normally do. Results of yield, disease susceptibility, growth characteristics and quality can be fould on this web page. Additional links for further results and administrative data can be found as well.
